[30;1m31 | [0m[35m        Saves model and trainer state at the end of each completed epoch.[0m
[30;1m32 | [0m[35m    save_every_num_seconds : `int`, optional (default=`None`)[0m
[30;1m33 | [0m[35m        If set, makes sure we never go longer than this number of seconds between saving a model.[0m
[30;1m34 | [0m[35m    save_every_num_batches : `int`, optional (default=`None`)[0m

[30;1m67 | [0m[35m    A `DatasetReader` knows how to turn a file containing a dataset into a collection[0m
